==Ancient Greek==

===Etymology===
From [[μετά]] {{GG|3326}} and [[μορφόω]] {{GG|3445}}

===Pronunciation===
*μεταμορφόω / metamorphoō / met-am-or-fo'-o

===Verb===
'''μεταμορφόω'''

# to transform (literally or figuratively “metamorphose”): - change, transfigure, transform.

